    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "u said it's \"essential\" though... isn't that a bit strong? i thought there were plenty of other ways people suggest fixing things, like just going 100% solar and wind? why would it be essential instead of just one of many options?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
